/**
 * Agent Life catalog registry API.
 *
 * This module is the metadata spine for editor-visible placeable objects. It
 * keeps catalog entries, normalized categories/tags, aliases, editor visibility,
 * and runtime scale/action adapters behind one read-only registry contract.
 * It does not place objects, create colliders, persist state, or route agents.
 */
